<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Deputy Traffic Commissioner made orders to:</p>

<p>refuse the application made by P Elsagood Transport Services Ltd for a standard international operator’s licence fir 4 vehicles and 4 trailers.</p>

<p>The decision was made on 25 October 2018.</p>

<p>An appeal was made to the Upper Tribunal on this decision and was dismissed on the 4 April 2019.</p>
</div>
</div>

